{
  "stem": "26609.7",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 18.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I thought, now here they'll find me out, and here they will kill me.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I've seen something else there that I'll tell later.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And there was a huge queue, going into the-- before they sent us to Germany, they had to, one by one, to-- eh-- I think they had to enlist them all-- all the people.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And because not everybody there was sent to Germany-- all to the same place.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I waited.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I thought, no-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I'll tell later how I got to the prison.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It's always-- I have a method.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I always thought-- I don't know-- I learned it during the war-- not to go the first, but the last-- always the last.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "First, see what will happen for the others.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I didn't want the others to see what happens to me, if they find out.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I will be the last.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I waited.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Whenever a one came, I let them all before me, to go in-- one by one, went into the office.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I-- until I was the last.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I went in.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I thought, now is my last-- not my hour, my last two minutes.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They will kill me here.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But I was surprised.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I came in there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Behind the desk, who sits there?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The man-- the Ukrainian who went over to the Germans, who worked with our-- who paid us the wages-- [INAUDIBLE], or whoever-- at the laboratorium where I worked, who knew me very well.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he was sitting behind the desk.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I came in.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And as I seen him, my knees were so-- got soft.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I thought, now I'll faint here.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Don't faint, I told myself.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Be strong.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Don't faint.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You'll see what happens.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You wait.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Rather, wait.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
